{"tid":2218616,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"華府公布制裁11中港官員細節，不得與相關人士掌管部門交易","createTime":"2020-09-26T10:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T11:22:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e779fa1715f67071ba18aed0975156ab39b8c9ce","tid":2218616,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WezuCmQuZr4BJ1lQAnXtRw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/1997dbe57fdaf66af4ef95242cac7aec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWezuCmQuZr4BJ1lQAnXtRw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F1997dbe57fdaf66af4ef95242cac7aec&h=6526cf81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu6RE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=62046a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】美國財政部於8月宣布制裁11名中港官員，包括特首林鄭月娥等人，指他們損害香港自治。財政部周五（25日）公布制裁令的執行細節，列明美國人不得與受制裁人士掌管的部門交易。<br />\n<br />\n財政部發出「常見問題F&amp;Q 840號」文件，說明在中港官員受制裁下，只要制裁對象沒有直接或間接參與，美國人可繼續與制裁對象任職或控制的香港政府部門進行常規往來。<br />\n<br />\n此外，華府亦禁止美國人與制裁對象交易、處理他們的物業或物業利益，包括任何由一名或更多受制裁人士直接或間接持有50%權益的實體。財政部提醒美國人在與制裁對象任職的港府部門來往時，應注意確保自己沒有在未經外國資產管理辦公室（OFAC）批准下，與相關人士進行直接或間接交易。不過，美國人可以訂立與港府非受制裁官員簽署的合約，而該官員應獲港府授權簽訂相關合約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QVAK4BXv2YwT.sIQtvUW5w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/2cf2e5e3525969779343f2d3551d304b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQVAK4BXv2YwT.sIQtvUW5w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F2cf2e5e3525969779343f2d3551d304b&h=d37a8fca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da44a01efdd2c3dc9df698199a7732266c689876","tid":2218616,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"上個月邊間銀行 出糧畀佢哋"}]}